{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DELEARNIA HELPS YOU ENJOY MATH AGAIN</h2>Delearnia: Fractions of Hope is a\u00a0story-driven\u00a0adventure puzzle game\u00a0with\u00a0a mysterious\u00a0world\u00a0and\u00a0a touch of mathematics. It's a short Metroidvania... or\u00a0<strong>Mathroidvania</strong>?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426990/extras/dlr-gif2.gif?t=1733395932\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HERE, MATH HAS A PURPOSE</h2>Solve unique puzzles in your own way by combining logical thinking and math. Make your way through the various obstacles and boss battles with mathemagical spells. Unlock new skills and try different strategies in your attempts to defeat your foes. Meanwhile, you'll become more confident at handling numbers and solving math problems.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426990/extras/dlr-gif1.gif?t=1733395932\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MATH IS A MYSTERY</h2>By chance, you become trapped in an otherworldly place,\u00a0<strong>Delearnia</strong>. A world once happy and welcoming, but not anymore. This world needs healing. It needs\u00a0<strong>you</strong>.<br><br><strong>Explore</strong> the\u00a0dreamlike interconnected\u00a0world. Meet and interact with the residents of Delearnia. They will help you unravel the secrets of Delearnia.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2426990/extras/dlr-gifs4.gif?t=1733395932\" /><br><strong>&quot;Hope is not gone. It's just broken and trapped. Fractioned. Hidden away.&quot;</strong><br><br><strong>Tags:</strong> Delearnia, fractions, learn fractions, educational game, math learning, math game, learn math","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to Delearnia","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2426990/2a79514f6c224296ef38bafab67347d4c6e49831.jpg"},{"name":"Big R